      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/652816311_17903540652389635_5522817285720914569_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDc1NDI3NDY5MzkxMTMwMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=6m5mGH3WNnMQ7kNvwFFRebw&amp;_nc_oc=AdoMENH5nqcxfndv99u0LrLA6x45j-zI1k1snQ_9go1kah0u53e9vBpu1W0PkjOG9kU&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6eyA3PEgANBL4D1CZW2VGw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzR_b9QGBD3TJGDGoLetQZH4LswMy7qf4L6t2_sRRSSow&amp;oe=69CA0062" alt="Slide 1 fra @anni.vestergaard" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/652178924_17903540649389635_6762046995803633582_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDc1NDI3NzU1NDQyODUyNQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=JCjr4UuOf3MQ7kNvwFIGK0j&amp;_nc_oc=AdpLIPjHwB6UdAyewLV9T2Xj-EWJQiM-4HhgMsIsUhhBFdSw7gXseTeK9HgrRYJx6iU&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6eyA3PEgANBL4D1CZW2VGw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzTLVOsPlC-p2pAJNfrUMXU5sQYxmiAUs1M7DV3lAb1vg&amp;oe=69C9F9A4" alt="Slide 2 fra @anni.vestergaard" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654080892_17903540661389635_995882639686187901_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDc1NDI4MDU0OTE3NTQwMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=WQayeFEVCzgQ7kNvwFX88xk&amp;_nc_oc=AdpSp2yLH-tB5RNVYzruq1SDeIg8WzLP_Y9zoFiUoPAcxyLCgbS8MfQbo8cby6RbuxI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6eyA3PEgANBL4D1CZW2VGw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzV0g_rO_6xKmMJJn68pGO6G6wcf6ykCqKHStSfVOi4Jw&amp;oe=69C9F819" alt="Slide 3 fra @anni.vestergaard" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653694070_17903540679389635_2998004934902237358_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDc1NDI4MjkzOTk0MDQyOQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=k91l-Ncmf3sQ7kNvwGOesqZ&amp;_nc_oc=Ado2ccXtyMUbDRdF1uskt-7OMatTf7XkT2Y_oyWsQnBWJ6cEvZ3dUrfdPs6gOD1C8Pc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6eyA3PEgANBL4D1CZW2VGw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwgxZxI9korcLCzRCsBjKZLWWbdBkgjrtzSp-P8fuUaHA&amp;oe=69C9FDFB" alt="Slide 4 fra @anni.vestergaard" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (8 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@anni.vestergaard</strong></p><p>LIMBO – VEJEN HJEM / LIMBO – GOING HOME has been selected for Årets Bedste Bogarbejde 2026 / Best Book Design 2026<br/>
 <br/>
The design of this artist’s book is made in close collaboration with visual artist and filmmaker Jytte Rex, editor Maja Gro Gundersen, and graphic design studio Anni’s.<br/>
<br/>
The correspondence between image and text is a core element in Rex’s artistic practice across visual art, film and artists’ books. In her work and in the book, Rex draws on literature as a conversation partner throughout her life as an artist. She uses this fact as a point of departure, composing an artist’s book combining pieces of literature with sequences of her own images, old and new.<br/>
<br/>
The book format refers to literature (rather than an art catalogue), and the intention has been to create a book object that could be experienced as a work of art in and of itself.<br/>
<br/>
In contrast to the classic typography inside the book, the title on the cover is handwritten by the artist herself and printed in silver foil. The handwriting marks a connection to her early works and its origin in the art of the 60s and 70s with its preoccupation with the informal and the everyday. The handwriting also links to Rex’s pioneering work within feminist art.<br/>
<br/>
Choosing the soft and tactile book cover material, the book underlines the sensory aspect of the work felt strongly in the photographic image of hands chosen by Rex for the cover.<br/>
<br/>
Congratulation to the team behind the book and thank you @boghåndværk<br/>
 <br/>
Design: @anni.vestergaard  Editor: @majagro  Press: @narayanapress</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DV-3UQADI3e/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
